Event15 = "There is another bright flash and a thunderous rumble. The water is...\nGone. The walls are dry, the window is intact and your partner is nowhere in sight. You fear that you might have gone insane or that the brain damage is playing tricks on you.\nNo answer comforts you and you fall asleep crying that day. Two days since your.. vision pass by, seemingly the same.\n\nUntil one day.\n\nThere is a knock on the door and after a few seconds, the nurse quietly walks in with sorrow in her eyes.\nA seed of worry begins to sprout in the back of your head.\n"
Option1 = "Ask what is wrong."
Option2 = "Say nothing."

